"When you create a `lib` project with `cargo new` it creates a file `src/lib."
"rs` with some default code. Edit that file and replace the default code with "
"the code below. As mentioned, we will implement a slightly modified version "
"of [the guessing game from The Rust Book](https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/"
"ch02-00-guessing-game-tutorial.html). Instead of implementing as a `bin` "
"crate, we're using a `lib` and will expose the main logic as a Python "
"function."
